### Hadith 1:391

*Narrated Ibn Abbas:*

When the Prophet entered the Ka'ba, he invoked Allah in each and every
side of it and did not pray till he came out of it, and offered a
two-Rak'at prayer facing the Ka'ba and said, "This is the Qibla."

